Description
-----------

Disables loading textures and sounds at level loadings.

Usage
-----

At the console type...

    com_QuickLoad [flag]

Parameters
----------

-   [flag]
    -   0 - Load maps as usual.
    -   1 - Don't load any textures or sounds.
    -   2 - Don't load any textures.
    -   3 - Don't load any sounds.

